name: Wmf-mobile-redirector
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This mobile redirector plugin will redirect mobile & tablet devices to the your mobile site. WMF Mobile Redirector created for WMF Framework & Webbu Mobile Themes.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Authors and Contributors
Webbu
